151
00:09:57,599 --> 00:09:58,850
- Yes, you are!
- Bravo!

152
00:09:58,934 --> 00:10:00,644
I've received numerous prizes.

153
00:10:00,727 --> 00:10:01,895
He has.

154
00:10:01,979 --> 00:10:04,565
