Final warning!

164
00:10:25,002 --> 00:10:28,213
In insulting me, you
insult the dramatic muse.

165
00:10:28,297 --> 00:10:32,384
And worse, you... you
desecrate this theater...

166
00:10:32,467 --> 00:10:36,013
this crucible of human...

