just be able to tell her</i>

803
00:43:34,449 --> 00:43:37,578
<i>What it's like when I see her</i>

804
00:43:41,123 --> 00:43:42,874
<i>It's something like</i>

805
00:43:42,958 --> 00:43:44,042
<i>Happiness</i>

806
00:43:44,126 --> 00:43:45,836
<i>It's something like</i>

807
00:43:45,919 --> 00:43:47,129
<i>Hunger</i>

808
00:43:47,212 --> 00:43:48,714
<i>And something like</i>

809
00:43:48,797 --> 00:43:51,049
<i>Fear</i>

810
00:43:51,133 --> 00:43:55,846
<i>I'd give anything for someone to say</i>

811
