<i>Have you ever loved someone</i>

1826
01:51:50,712 --> 01:51:53,006
<i>Madly</i>

1827
01:51:56,885 --> 01:51:59,555
<i>It's okay, Roxanne</i>

1828
01:51:59,638 --> 01:52:02,307
<i>I've known what I am</i>

1829
01:52:02,391 --> 01:52:06,895
<i>From the second your eyes held mine</i>

1830
01:52:09,189 --> 01:52:11,233
<i>Ever since then</i>

1831
01:52:11,316 --> 01:52:14,486
<i>I've been a patient man</i>

1832
