<i>So, no, Cyrano</i>

1837
01:52:35,882 --> 01:52:38,844
<i>I won't let you go</i>

1838
01:52:38,927 --> 01:52:43,974
<i>Love's a painful painful game</i>

1839
01:52:45,767 --> 01:52:47,227
You love me.

1840
01:52:48,312 --> 01:52:49,313
Yes.

1841
